In Anthridercynantide a street worker gathers all his savings to go abroad and face a woman who he believes shares a common past with him.

This title is an original ATP Projects release, published 2011-08-03. The photography, writing, production and direction was done by mikey. The character art was done by lordcloudx. The title uses the Ren'Py engine created and modified by PyTom. The music was composed by evo. Estimated completion time is 20 minutes .

Anthridercynantide is game Nr. 20 of the Original 22.
